==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Traverse drill
<hw>Trav"erse drill</hw>. <fld>(Mach.)</fld> <def>A machine tool for
drilling slots, in which the work or tool has a lateral motion back and
forth; also, a drilling machine in which the spindle holder can be
adjusted laterally.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Traverser</ent>⟦br⟧
